add write_s function in cmdq helper functions which
writes a constant value to address with large dma
access support.

Signed-off-by: Dennis YC Hsieh <dennis-yc.hsieh@mediatek.com>
Reviewed-by: CK Hu <ck.hu@mediatek.com>
